n="00:19.043" end="00:19.274">one</span> <span begin="00:19.274" end="00:20.329">else</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我与他人共度的时光 都是徒然浪费</span></p><p begin="00:21.803" end="00:24.439" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:21.803" end="00:22.203">She</span> <span begin="00:22.203" end="00:22.421">was</span><span begin="00:22.421" end="00:22.586">n't</span> <span begin="00:22.642" end="00:22.942">e</span><span begin="00:22.942" end="00:23.066">ven</span> <span begin="00:23.193" end="00:23.614">half</span> <span begin="00:23.614" end="00:24.115">of</span> <span begin="00:24.115" end="00:24.439">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">她甚至不及你半分</span></p><p begin="00:25.628" end="00:27.938" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:25.628" end="00:25.871">Rem</span><span begin="00:25.871" end="00:26.111">i</span><span begin="00:26.111" end="00:26.638">niscin'</span> <span begin="00:26.638" end="00:26.833">how</span> <span begin="00:26.833" end="00:27.075">you</span> <span begin="00:27.075" end="00:27.938">felt</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:28.042" end="00:29.762"><span begin="00:28.042" end="00:28.559">(-niscin'</span> <span begin="00:28.559" end="00:28.776">how</span> <span begin="00:28.776" end="00:28.972">you</span> <span begin="00:28.972" end="00:29.762">felt)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">想着你当初的感觉</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">回想着你当初的感觉</span></p><p begin="00:30.671" end="00:35.751" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:30.671" end="00:30.939">And</span> <span begin="00:30.939" end="00:31.470">e</span><span begin="00:31.470" end="00:31.918">ven</span> <span begin="00:31.918" end="00:32.261">though</span> <span begin="00:33.651" end="00:33.891">you</span> <span begin="00:33.891" end="00:34.141">put</span> <span begin="00:34.141" end="00:34.410">my</span> <span begin="00:34.410" end="00:34.631">life</span> <span begin="00:34.631" end="00:34.936">through</span> <span begin="00:34.936" end="00:35.751">hell</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">尽管你让我的人生坠入地狱</span></p><p begin="00:37.547" end="00:40.877" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:37.547" end="00:37.802">I</span> <span begin="00:37.802" end="00:38.002">can't</span> <span begin="00:38.002" end="00:38.212">seem</span> <span begin="00:38.271" end="00:38.394">to</span> <span begin="00:38.515" end="00:38.732">for</span><span begin="00:38.781" end="00:39.151">get</span> <span begin="00:39.301" end="00:39.743">'bout</span> <span begin="00:39.743" end="00:40.042">you,</span> <span begin="00:40.254" end="00:40.706">'bout</span> <span begin="00:40.706" end="00:40.877">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我依然对你念念不忘</span></p><p begin="00:41.479" end="00:43.631" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:41.479" end="00:41.729">I</span> <span begin="00:41.729" end="00:41.931">want</span> <span begin="00:41.931" end="00:42.135">you</span> <span begin="00:42.135" end="00:42.323">to</span> <span begin="00:42.421" end="00:42.639">my</span><span begin="00:42.639" end="00:43.631">self</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">全身心地渴望着你</span></p><p begin="00:45.353" end="00:49.709" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:45.353" end="00:45.610">And</span> <span begin="00:45.610" end="00:45.835">now</span> <span begin="00:45.835" end="00:46.081">I'm</span> <span begin="00:46.081" end="00:46.361">ask</span><span begin="00:46.361" end="00:46.559">in',</span> <span begin="00:46.559" end="00:46.690">who</span> <span begin="00:46.690" end="00:46.956">do</span> <span begin="00:46.956" end="00:47.277">you</span> <span begin="00:47.306" end="00:47.552">be</span><span begin="00:47.552" end="00:47.901">long</span> <span begin="00:48.009" end="00:48.462">to</span> <span begin="00:48.531" end="00:49.709">now?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我心中疑问 此刻谁拥有着你？</span></p><p begin="00:50.470" end="00:53.621" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:50.470" end="00:50.704">Who</span> <span begin="00:50.704" end="00:50.896">you</span> <span begin="00:50.945" end="00:51.149">give</span> <span begin="00:51.198" end="00:51.409">that</span> <span begin="00:51.448" end="00:51.850">love</span> <span begin="00:51.886" end="00:52.417">to</span> <span begin="00:52.417" end="00:53.621">now?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你的爱给了谁？</span></p><p begin="00:54.378" end="00:57.738" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:54.378" end="00:54.572">Who</span> <span begin="00:54.572" end="00:54.827">you</span> <span begin="00:54.903" end="00:55.299">pullin'</span> <span begin="00:55.341" end="00:56.317">u</span><span begin="00:56.317" end="00:57.738">p on?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你会去谁那里拜访？</span></p><p begin="00:58.282" end="01:01.304" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:58.282" end="00:58.536">Who</span> <span begin="00:58.536" end="00:58.719">you</span> <span begin="00:58.771" end="00:59.002">get</span><span begin="00:59.002" end="00:59.175">tin'</span> <span begin="00:59.175" end="00:59.679">sprung</span> <span begin="00:59.783" end="01:00.183">for</span> <span begin="01:00.222" end="01:01.304">now?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你为谁而买醉？</span></p><p begin="01:01.935" end="01:05.527" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:01.935" end="01:02.127">And</span> <span begin="01:02.127" end="01:02.421">what</span> <span begin="01:02.421" end="01:02.674">they</span> <span begin="01:02.674" end="01:02.908">got</span> <span begin="01:02.908" end="01:03.159">that</span> <span begin="01:03.159" end="01:03.389">I</span> <span begin="01:03.389" end="01:03.644">ain't</span> <span begin="01:03.644" end="01:03.898">got?</span> <span begin="01:03.898" end="01:04.138">'Cause</span> <span begin="01:04.138" end="01:04.634">I</span> <span begin="01:04.634" end="01:04.869">got</span> <span begin="01:04.869" end="01:05.094">a</span> <span begin="01:05.094" end="01:05.527">lot</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他有哪些我没有的特点？我明明也不赖</span></p><p begin="01:05.833" end="01:09.498" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:05.833" end="01:06.094">Don't</span> <span begin="01:06.094" end="01:06.324">make</span> <span begin="01:06.324" end="01:06.571">me</span> <span begin="01:06.571" end="01:06.805">run</span> <span begin="01:06.805" end="01:07.058">up</span> <span begin="01:07.058" end="01:07.300">on</span> <span begin="01:07.300" end="01:07.538">'em,</span> <span begin="01:07.538" end="01:07.783">got</span> <span begin="01:07.783" end="01:07.990">me</span> <span begin="01:08.055" end="01:08.279">blow</span><span begin="01:08.279" end="01:08.538">in'</span> <span begin="01:08.538" end="01:08.749">up</span> <span begin="01:08.749" end="01:08.978">their</span> <span begin="01:08.978" end="01:09.498">spot</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可别让我沿路追上他 轰了他的地盘</span></p><p begin="01:09.799" end="01:13.519" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:09.799" end="01:09.981">'Cause</span> <span begin="01:09.981" end="01:10.210">I</span> <span begin="01:10.210" end="01:10.473">ain't</span> <span begin="01:10.473" end="01:10.719">got</span> <span begin="01:10.719" end="01:10.912">no</span> <span begin="01:11.010" end="01:11.287">busi</span><span begin="01:11.287" end="01:11.505">ness</span> <span begin="01:11.505" end="01:11.737">catch</span><span begin="01:11.737" end="01:11.937">in'</span> <span begin="01:11.937" end="01:12.225">feel</span><span begin="01:12.225" end="01:12.507">ings</span> <span begin="01:12.507" end="01:12.930">any</span><span begin="01:12.930" end="01:13.519">way</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我根本不需要在乎内心的感觉</span></p><p begin="01:13.906" end="01:16.829" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:13.906" end="01:14.147">I</span> <span begin="01:14.147" end="01:14.382">ain't</span> <span begin="01:14.382" end="01:14.664">got</span> <span begin="01:14.664" end="01:14.971">no</span> <span begin="01:14.971" end="01:15.149">busi</span><span begin="01:15.149" end="01:15.389">ness</span> <span begin="01:15.389" end="01:15.632">catch</span><span begin="01:15.632" end="01:15.855">in'</span> <span begin="01:15.855" end="01:16.130">feel</span><span begin="01:16.130" end="01:16.829">ings</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不需要把握什么感觉</span></p><p begin="01:17.250" end="01:18.958" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:17.250" end="01:17.547">Catch</span><span begin="01:17.547" end="01:17.820">in'</span> <span begin="01:17.820" end="01:18.108">feel</span><span begin="01:18.108" end="01:18.958">ings</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">把握感觉</span></p><p begin="01:19.747" end="01:22.610" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:19.747" end="01:19.992">These</span> <span begin="01:19.992" end="01:20.292">girls</span> <span begin="01:20.292" end="01:20.694">only</span> <span begin="01:20.694" end="01:20.918">want</span> <span begin="01:20.918" end="01:21.201">you</span> <span begin="01:21.201" end="01:21.448">when</span> <span begin="01:21.448" end="01:21.679">you're</span> <span begin="01:21.679" end="01:21.909">win</span><span begin="01:21.909" end="01:22.610">nin'</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:22.701" end="01:23.671"><span begin="01:22.701" end="01:22.811">(Win</span><span begin="01:22.919" end="01:23.671">nin')</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">功成名就</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这些姑娘们只看上了我的功成名就</span></p><p begin="01:23.671" end="01:26.421" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:23.671" end="01:23.861">But</span> <span begin="01:23.861" end="01:24.090">you've</span> <span begin="01:24.090" end="01:24.358">been</span> <span begin="01:24.358" end="01:24.602">with</span> <span begin="01:24.602" end="01:24.873">me</span> <span begin="01:24.873" end="01:25.111">from</span> <span begin="01:25.111" end="01:25.351">the</span> <span begin="01:25.351" end="01:25.585">be</span><span begin="01:25.585" end="01:25.865">gin</span><span begin="01:25.865" end="01:26.421">nin'</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:26.439" end="01:27.474"><span begin="01:26.439" end="01:26.581">(Ooh,</span> <span begin="01:26.581" end="01:26.914">yeah,</span> <span begin="01:27.094" end="01:27.474">yeah)</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可自始至终与我在一起的人是你</span></p><p begin="01:27.539" end="01:30.354" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:27.539" end="01:27.819">And</span> <span begin="01:27.819" end="01:28.070">I</span> <span begin="01:28.070" end="01:28.291">know</span> <span begin="01:28.291" end="01:28.543">right</span> <span begin="01:28.543" end="01:28.823">now</span> <span begin="01:28.823" end="01:29.063">that</span> <span begin="01:29.063" end="01:29.326">we're</span> <span begin="01:29.326" end="01:29.531">not</span> <span begin="01:29.531" end="01:29.845">talk</span><span begin="01:29.845" end="01:30.354">in'</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:30.225" end="01:31.231"><span begin="01:30.225" end="01:30.419">(Not</span> <span begin="01:30.419" end="01:30.668">talk</span><span begin="01:30.723" end="01:31.231">in')</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">已经疏远</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我也知道 现在的我们已经疏远</span></p><p begin="01:31.285" end="01:35.165" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:31.285" end="01:31.426">I</span> <span begin="01:31.426" end="01:31.666">hope</span> <span begin="01:31.725" end="01:31.956">you</span> <span begin="01:31.956" end="01:32.181">know</span> <span begin="01:32.181" end="01:32.440">this</span> <span begin="01:32.440" end="01:32.685">dick</span> <span begin="01:32.685" end="01:32.859">i</span><span begin="01:32.859" end="01:32.994">s s</span><span begin="01:32.994" end="01:33.152">til</span><span begin="01:3